# Content / CMS Rules

Pages CMS edits Git-backed content files.
Cloudflare stores heavy job/project photos.
Content stores image URLs and metadata.

Every image object should include:
- src
- alt
- caption when useful
- type: before | after | detail | process
- service
- location
- featured boolean when needed

Services need:
- title
- slug
- seoTitle
- metaDescription
- heroTitle
- summary
- includedServices
- priceFactors
- process
- faqs
- bookingType: direct-book | quote-request | assessment | call-only

Service-area pages must be unique and locally useful.
Do not generate thin city doorway pages.
